ClassifierResult(Map item) {
  this._classifierId = item["classifier_id"] ?? "";
  this._name = item["name"] ?? "";
  _classes = new List<ClassResult>();
  for (Map result in item["classes"]) {
    _classes.add(new ClassResult(result));
  }
}
